	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The timer could go to the CPU's reset or maybe it does something with the CIC (if present). You could just remove the circuit and connect a switch to the reset line (or tie it to VCC if you never need to reset.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
